                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="text-decoration: underline">Server Sets:</span>
<br />
In regards to new PvP server, I think we have enough servers (TZ, RZ, VZ, and SZ). They need to recode one to Guildwar. The other, Racewar. And one Good vs Evil. And leave one FFA. Make PoK, PoT, and Nexus PvP zones. Give melees channeling. NO FV ruleset, people will still bag gear. PvP immunity until level 10 (you cant attack or be attacked). 8 Level up / down range for PvP. Scale resists accordingly, and buffs.
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">PvP (and minor PvE):</span>
<br />
Group Shielding (still overwritten by Focus, obviously).
<br />
Upgraded Umbra Series (make the AC150 or 200 self only).
<br />
Increase Mana Seive capability, and Theft of Thought drain against a PC.
<br />
Remove "mana giving" component in Wandering Mind & Scryer Trespass, or make it noticablely better. 
<br />
Upgraded version of Torment spells, which give mana + HP (level 65).
<br />
Decrease recast time on Bounce series.
<br />
Allow AoE mez / stun to ignore a groupmembers pet on PvP servers.
<br />
A new Tash series, for insert_random_resist. Dispellable.
<br />
Lower the recast of Doppleganger, allow it to cast spells youve memmed.
<br />
Give Ench a new nuke or DoT series (in line w/ a new Tash).
<br />
Retool the resist system to prevent a full blown resist against someone w/ 100 MR.
<br />
Allow charmed mobs to resist dispel by enemy NPCs & PCs.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
